data.description: Less than 4 blocks from Bayview Park... this open plan, three bedroom two & half bath, East Hill home now features over 2300 sf of living area after an 1100 sf addition was finished in 2005. The renovation and addition, seamlessly combine the desirability of a modern open floor-plan with the style of a 1940's cottage! This flexible floor plan is great for someone that wants a home office...or possible 4th bedroom as well! It also has a large master bedroom with private bath ... The kitchen has old Chicago style brick floors, lots of cabinet space, large island with breakfast bar. The master bedroom is very spacious with a bay window, large cedar storage bench and sitting area between 2 large his/hers closets. The master bath is also large with a separate shower, bath tub and 2 sinks. Out back there is a screened porch with hot tub...open deck...one car garage, and just enough grass to make everyone happy! Call today for your appointment to see this fine East Hill home!
